178)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106178)\">Ex. 22:25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106235\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106235)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106235)\">Lev. 25:36<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112428\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112428)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112428)\">Hel. 4:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110414\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110414)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110414)\">1 Pet. 1:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114145\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114145)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114145)\">D&amp;C 61:38<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114355\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114355)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114355)\">D&amp;C 73:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}